Q: 注册号为OE-HWM的飞机的制造年份是什么？
SQL: SELECT make_year FROM aircraft_details WHERE registration = "OE-HWM";
actual_SQL:
SELECT make_year
FROM aircraft_details
WHERE pure_reg = 'oehwm'
LIMIT 50;
